metadata.name: NAGAS x HANUMAAN
metadata.description:
This is the art of Thailand that has been redesigned by myself. Mix of Japanese art Feels like a Japanese tattoo

Hanuman is The Monkey king of Thai literature. it is an albino monkey. It is very powerful. When the power is manifested, there will be 8 arms, immortal when fighting until near death or defeat. Just the wind blows and it will rise again.

Nagas is a Giant serpent in the legend of Buddhism and Thailand. is the god of water live in an underground cave very powerful diamond scales able to transform And it is very sacred to people in the eastern part of Thailand.
